{"tid":1821243,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"西灣河堵路 防暴驅散","createTime":"2020-01-12T06:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T06:30:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d377e11b2e5b5fe6c09ec6d4c49b205d304c8d45","tid":1821243,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T06:25:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200112/Q4BBICFA6HYJMQD44BDSCZITKA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200112%2FQ4BBICFA6HYJMQD44BDSCZITKA%2F&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXS1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=5459921d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200112%2FQ4BBICFA6HYJMQD44BDSCZITKA%2F&h=9e0a7a27\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200112/Q4BBICFA6HYJMQD44BDSCZITKA/</a><br />\n<br />\n西灣河堵路 防暴驅散<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200112/large/1578761241_49c9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200112%2Flarge%2F1578761241_49c9.gif&h=aff7c080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西灣河有示威者堵路，大批防暴警到場戒備。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】網民昨發起「全城連儂日」，在全港18區張貼文宣，晚上有人在西灣河用雪糕筒堵路阻塞交通，又毀壞交通燈，大批防暴警到場驅散示威者並清理路障。<br />\n<br />\n現場是港鐵西灣河站對出十字路口，為去年11月11日有黑衣示威者被一名警員開真槍擊中的位置。昨晚9時許，有示威者將雪糕筒放在路上堵路，有交通燈亦遭破壞。一批防暴警到場驅散，示威者隨即離去。防暴警清走路障，並手持防暴槍和圓盾，在筲箕灣道的行人路及安全島上戒備。部份街坊在場圍觀，現場亦泊有至少五輛警車，防暴警要求在太安街行人路聚集的街坊離開，警察之後又一字排開在行人天橋入口戒備。至晚上近10時許，防暴警陸續登上旅遊巴離開，事件中無人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n■記者司徒韋桐"},{"pid":"66acf93efe310f2f8a05e519b085311928ee7c4a","tid":1821243,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T06:30:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">灣仔:《臨時自治區》座談會+新書派發</span><br />\n時間 ： 1400-1600<br />\n地點 ：灣仔艺鵠書店ACO Books<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">2020 港共受刑 天下制裁 遊行前集氣大會</span><br />\n時間 ： 1500-1700<br />\n地點 ：愛丁堡廣場<br />\n(<span style=\"color: orange;\">已獲不反對通知書</span>)"}]}